Hello everyone,
i need help on how to filter in a multi-select. I know that for a select you do, for example, like this:
{% if request.query_dict.content_type in ["1", "2", "3", "4", "5", "6", "7", "8", "9"]%}
     {% set queryparam = queryparam ~ "&amp; content_type =" ~ request.query_dict.content_type | urlencode%}
{% endif%}
but I don't really know how to do it for a multi-select.
Thanks
